Where Can i download this for free?

By Lisa Shock on Monday, October 25, 2010 - 06:05 am:

You can't. It wasn't a downloadable game, it was an online game hosted on Korean servers. You had to register to get the download that gave you access. Since it's all been taken down, there's no way to get the download, and, even if you could get it (I still have the software on my computer.) there's nothing you could do with it because the game itself isn't running anymore.
